{"tid":1308600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香 港 人一 齊 守 連 儂 牆","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T02:42:50.000Z","uid":102378,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5fb9432b854939c62139b0844ae78303a8a787","tid":1308600,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母丫</span></span><br />\n守乜鬼連儂牆<br />\n守牆 只會比人日日減血<br />\n如果有手足再比人打 <br />\n只會增加人民鬥人民意識<br />\n對反政府更加冇幫助<br />\n<br />\nMemo紙痴過好易ja<br />\n比班廢老撕 撕完 第二日再痴<br />\n鬥長命 鬥耐性<br />\n無謂因為咁起沖突 <br />\n人民鬥人民 對運動冇著數<br />\n<br />\n大家記住<br />\n革命一方 <br />\n只適合遊擊 快速攻擊<br />\n唔適合守地 <br />\n學魚蛋革命 鐵馬都唔用 唔守地<br />\n咪再將雨革d野帶落黎<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我冇野講\n1. 立即撤回送中條例\n2. 除消暴動定義\n3. 不再追究義士\n4. 成立獨立調查\n5. 真雙普選</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ae44121c1a5c8315df52792f0a077a17230adf2b","tid":1308600,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"[拆一掛十] 連儂牆意義在於被毀及重建<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304033</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d656f78837abc7ea6c9751bcbf98e0f36bd7e0f4","tid":1308600,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:40:13.000Z","msg":"1. 立即撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 除消暴動定義<br />\n3. 不再追究義士<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查<br />\n5. 真雙普選"},{"pid":"6c17452dd4dda09a2ae16b4810d1a5b459e101cb","tid":1308600,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:40:47.000Z","msg":"[策略] 連儂牆宜貼不宜守<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1304314/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1304314/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n整完連儂牆唔好即時打卡 咁樣只會令對家更容易拆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1306264/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1306264/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"847dacc451b46ecddd5caa4f95b3f291d30806c4","tid":1308600,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:41:28.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7eef7852233ab443d4876c42f5ac0c18a496f8f8","tid":1308600,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"你地班仆街仔 <br />\n一齊講一次5大訴求<br />\n1. 立即撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 除消暴動定義<br />\n3. 不再追究義士<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查<br />\n5. 真雙普選"},{"pid":"9410f878c8d0e5a537b802a5378c6e32b53f2234","tid":1308600,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}